title: Teixeira Jardim (Dr. Arsénio)
body: He was born in Funchal on August 3, 1887, and is a medical surgeon from the Medical School of Lisbon, practicing clinical medicine in Monforte, in Alentejo. He is well known in both Portugal and Madeira as a specialist in diseases of the throat and ears. E.: Brief note on two cases of chronic tetanus, one generalized and the other localized, thesis, Lisbon, 1916, of 42 pages.
